    "active_lock_reason": null,
    "body": "`basic_usage.rst` claims:\n\n```\nModules may be loaded recursively with the ``load`` command's\n``--dependencies`` or ``-r`` argument:\n\n.. code-block:: sh\n\n    $ spack load --dependencies <spec> ...\n```\n\nThis is incorrect.  `spack module loads` has the recursive feature, but not `spack load`.  We should upgrade `spack load` with this feature.\n",
